 \lim \limits_{n \to \infty}(n^2e^{-1/n}+ne^{-1/n}-n^2) 
\exp(x)=\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\frac{x^{k}}{k!}
\lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}(n^{2}\exp(-1/n)+n\exp(-1/n)-n^{2})= \\ \lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\left(n^{2}\left(1-\frac{1}{n}+\frac{1}{2n^{2}}-\frac{1}{6n^{3}}\pm…\right)+n\left(1-\frac{1}{n}+\frac{1}{2n^{2}}-\frac{1}{6n^{3}}\pm…\right)-n^{2}\right)= \\ \lim_{n\rightarrow\infty}\left(n^{2}-n+\frac{1}{2}\pm O(\frac{1}{n^{k}})+n-1\pm O(\frac{1}{n^{k}})-n^{2}\right)= \\ =-\frac{1}{2} 
n^2
e^{-1/n} \approx~ 1-\frac{1}{n}+\frac{1}{2 n^2}-\frac{1}{6    n^3}+O\left(\left(\frac{1}{n}\right)^4\right)
n^2 e^{-1/n} + n e^{-1/n} - n^2 \approx-\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{3 n}-\frac{1}{8 n^2}+\frac{1}{30    n^3}+O\left(\left(\frac{1}{n}\right)^4\right)
x
e^x = 1+x + x^2/2+.....
e^{-1/n} \approx 1-\frac{1}{n}
n^2 e^{-1/n} + n e^{-1/n} - n^2 \approx n^2(1-\frac{1}{n} + \frac {1}{2n^2}...)+ n(1-\frac{1}{n}+ \frac {1}{2n^2}...) -n^2  = n^2 -n +\frac{1}{2}-... n -1 +\frac{1}{2n}....- n^2 =\frac{1}{2}-1=-\frac{1}{2}
